  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breaking and destroyed and big jumps!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a racing game to enjoy destruction, accidents, jumps, thrill, speed, and arcade-like gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fierce race on Japan's public roads!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can drive on courses in various situations, mainly on Japanese public roads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aim for the top of all courses!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the top of the race positions, the fastest time, and the largest amount of damages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Contents</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 types of cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 types of stages</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Genre</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade-like racing game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breaking and destroyed and big jumps!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a racing game to enjoy destruction, accidents, jumps, thrill, speed, and arcade-like gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A fierce race on Japan's public roads!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can drive on courses in various situations, mainly on Japanese public roads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aim for the top of all courses!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for the top of the race positions, the fastest time, and the largest amount of damages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Contents</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 types of cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 types of stages</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Genre</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade-like racing game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
